ABDI: Fuck you, old man!

40:52.609 --> 40:53.861
‐ Where the fuck is Ace?

40:53.861 --> 40:56.951
<i>[intense music]</i>

40:56.951 --> 40:59.665
<i>POP: Where's the body, Abdi?</i>

40:59.665 --> 41:02.629
[dog snarling, barking]

41:02.629 --> 41:04.340
<i>♪ ♪</i>

41:04.340 --> 41:06.386
<i>Where the fuck is Ace?</i>

41:06.386 --> 41:08.473
<i>♪ ♪</i>

41:08.473 --> 41:09.560
[dog yelps]

41:09.560 --> 41:10.979
<i>[music fades]</i>

41:10.979 --> 41:13.442
ABDI: [faintly] Pop!

41:13.442 --> 41:15.487
[shell clinks]

41:15.487 --> 41:18.493
[faint screaming
in foreign language]

41:18.493 --> 41:20.080
<i>♪ ♪</i>

