It's like we don't even exist.

42:18.573 --> 42:21.452
‐ You broke the rules,
little lady!

42:21.452 --> 42:23.916
[door latch clicks]

42:23.916 --> 42:26.170
[car door slams]

42:26.170 --> 42:28.759
[house door slams]

42:30.972 --> 42:33.686
[beetles buzzing]

42:36.692 --> 42:40.073
[beetles buzzing,
squelching on glass]

42:48.758 --> 42:51.764
[beetles buzzing, thudding]

42:51.764 --> 42:53.893
[beetle wings rustling]

42:53.893 --> 42:56.899
<i>[eerie music]</i>

